1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,290
You're home.

2
00:00:01,630 --> 00:00:03,630
You're still awake?

3
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:08,170
Didn't I tell you?
Let me know if you're going to be late.

4
00:00:08,630 --> 00:00:10,640
I was on a business trip.
I couldn't help coming home late.

5
00:00:10,640 --> 00:00:12,300
You still could've let me know.

6
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:13,680
I forgot, okay?

7
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:16,140
I worry that
something might have happened to you.

8
00:00:16,140 --> 00:00:16,930
My bad, my bad.

9
00:00:16,930 --> 00:00:18,770
I'm exhausted from the trip.

10
00:00:18,770 --> 00:00:22,020
Being tired is no excuse.

11
00:00:22,020 --> 00:00:23,820
Ugh, you're so annoying.

12
00:00:23,820 --> 00:00:25,070
Annoying?

13
00:00:25,070 --> 00:00:28,360
Yeah, you're too controlling.

14
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:30,860
Do I even have any freedom?

15
00:00:30,860 --> 00:00:33,280
Stop acting like my guardian.

16
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:36,080
What's wrong with an older brother
worrying about his younger brother?

17
00:00:36,080 --> 00:00:39,290
That's exactly what's so annoying.

18
00:00:39,290 --> 00:00:42,170
Besides, you're not even my real brother.

19
00:00:51,010 --> 00:00:54,930
Your scent has changed lately.

20
00:00:57,390 --> 00:00:58,430
What?

21
00:00:58,430 --> 00:01:00,390
It's Kamiki-san, isn't it?

22
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:02,900
You're with him every single day.

23
00:01:03,190 --> 00:01:05,610
Hinata!

24
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,620
That's enough.

25
00:01:17,790 --> 00:01:19,410
Mizuki!
